      y \u0111ang s\u1EAFc thu\u1ED1c r\u1ED3i!"
  - bongBongUI: {fileID: 932938606}
    txtNoiDung: {fileID: 297286985}
    noiDungThoai: "Kh\xF4ng k\u1ECBp n\u1EEFa r\u1ED3i... L\u1EA1i \u0111\xE2y...
      n\u1EAFm l\u1EA5y tay cha..."
  - bongBongUI: {fileID: 1986665956}
    txtNoiDung: {fileID: 1121778388}
    noiDungThoai: "H\xE0i nhi \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y. Ph\u1EE5 v\u01B0\u01A1ng c\xF3
      \u0111i\u1EC1u g\xEC r\u0103n d\u1EA1y?"
  - bongBongUI: {fileID: 932938606}
    txtNoiDung: {fileID: 297286985}
    noiDungThoai: "M\u1ED1i nh\u1EE5c n\u0103m x\u01B0a... cha ch\u01B0a m\u1ED9t
      ng\xE0y ngu\xF4i ngoai..."
  - bongBongUI: {fileID: 932938606}
    txtNoiDung: {fileID: 297286985}
    noiDungThoai: "Con... n\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng v\xEC cha m\xE0 l\u1EA5y \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      thi\xEAn h\u1EA1... th\xEC cha c\xF3 ch\u1EBFt d\u01B0\u1EDBi su\u1ED1i v\xE0ng
      c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 nh\u1EAFm m\u1EAFt!"
  - bongBongUI: {fileID: 1986665956}
    txtNoiDung: {fileID: 1121778388}
    noiDungThoai: "Ph\u1EE5 v\u01B0\u01A1ng..."
  - bongBongUI: {fileID: 932938606}
    txtNoiDung: {fileID: 297286985}
    noiDungThoai: "H\u1EE9a... h\u1EE9a v\u1EDBi cha..."
  - bongBongUI: {fileID: 1986665956}
    txtNoiDung: {fileID: 1121778388}
    noiDungThoai: "... H\xE0i nhi... xin kh\u1EAFc c\u1ED1t ghi t\xE2m."
  - bongBongUI: {fileID: 932938606}
